# Next.js 15 Rules

-   Use Server Components by default, only use 'use client' when necessary
-   Implement route handlers in app/api directory using Route Handlers API
-   Use Next.js's built-in SEO features with metadata objects
-   Leverage Server Actions for form submissions and data mutations
-   Use generateMetadata for dynamic metadata
-   Implement proper error handling with error.tsx files
-   Use loading.tsx for streaming and suspense
-   Use Next.js Image component for all images
-   Implement proper caching strategies using fetch cache options
